It has emerged that Choe Ryong－hae，... a top aide to North Korean leader Kim Jong－un，... may be related to the ruling Kim family.
South Korean news outlet YTN reported Friday，... quoting a high－ranking North Korean defector，... that Choe is the father－in law to Kim Jong－un′s younger sister Kim Yeo－jong.
There was speculation that Choe would be victim of a purge by Kim，... given his recent disappearance from public view，... but according to reports Thursday，... he has been sent to the north′s top school for re－education.
Reports on Kim Yeo－jong′s marriage with Choe′s second son have been circulating since early this year，...but the validity of those reports has been denied by South Korean government sources....
